TITLE: General Chemistry 04: Chemical Thermodynamics.
	- Pre-requisitives: General Chemistry 03: Chemical Reactions.
	- Co-requisitives: None.
	- Recommended: Thermodynamics 02.



Enthalpy of formation. Formal Def: Formation reaction. Hess Law. Examples.
Bond Enthalpy. Formal Def: Bond Breaking reaction.

Entropy of formation. Absolute Entropy.
Gibbs Free Energy. Spontaneity.
Gibbs Free Energy and the Reaction Quotient (mathematical relationship).

Chemical Thermodynamics: Internal Energy, Enthalpy, Entropy, Gibbs. Activation energy. Enthalpy-driven and entropy-driven.

Combustion Reactions.


